  "caseStudy": "<p>The actions of one firm in a market has a considerable effect on other firms.</p>",
  "hint": "INTERDEPENDENCE — each firm watching and reacting to a few big rivals — is the signature of one structure. (Most real candidates wrongly picked 'competitive'.)",
